new tools for the expertise of the car
in these days of bad weather , and accidents , the garages cars are not the only winner .
every day , thousands of cars , which have suffered a grim are brought up in a garage , where an expert to assess the damage and the cost of repairs .
each event is different , and the calculation of the cost cuts and the time of workforce could be a long and complex process .
calculating compensation to shoulder the cost of between 20,000 and 30,000 euros , including the parts and the workforce may take two or three hours .
on the other hand , with the assistance of the the latest computer tools , it would be a matter of minutes .
it is for this reason that almost 100 % of the experts to use this kind of systems .
service providers and solutions for the evaluation of the claims and maintenance are dedicated to collecting information from manufacturers , and then treat them and offer them to customers in the form of a useful tool .
in spain , audatex , leader of the usa solera , is the company ; 80 % of the assessments are made with its products .
other companies that compete in the field of tools to evaluate and providing information on the sector are gtmotive and eurotax .
the work with the information provided by the manufacturers is far from easy .
according to audatex eduardo velázquez , director of trade , the company in spain , with 63 manufacturers and importers , and every one of them provides them with information in a different format .
in addition , the amount of data to treat continues to increase , so that in the past five years , more than versions , variations and motorisations have been launched in the past 15 years .
when a new car lot on the market these businesses are at work .
it is a very hard work , because it must catalogue every thousand pieces of the vehicle and put his prize .
in addition , it sets a graphic image " smart " of each model on which we can click on different parts of a car to tourism .
if he is a model sold in huge numbers , the work can be ready in a week if they are moving very quickly .
if it is a little motor sold , it can take three or four months . now , audatex have information about 99,2 % of the cars sold in spain .
among the more exclusive models , for example , they have information about the porsche , but not of the ferrari and lamborghini .
on the vehicles on the road , a figure exceeds the 99 % .
for the job of documentation and preparing the databases , audatex has eight centers spread all over the world , spain , france , germany , the united states , brazil , mexico , china and japan , and all of them are specialized in some brands .
the national is located in alcobendas - madrid .
there , more than 100 technicians or general , experts in mechanical work simultaneously in three computer screens .
audatex invest 90 million per year to get these databases .
each month , 2.5 million data is stored , and the customers are actualisations every two days .
drafting of this huge flow of information to allow them to give them various uses , and to offer a variety of products .
the most frequent application for the repair and maintenance , but in different countries , there are also tools for the management of the components of or damage to calculate the value residual vénale or a car .
the only company that has a guide to making inquiries about the value of cars of opportunity eurotax in spain .
audatex do not offer in our countries , but in the united states .
in view of the products offered by audatex , it is easy to get an idea of the type of support it can provide to the workers in the sector .
this company provides 10 different tools , the flagship is audaplus evaluation standard , the solution of the fires , for experts .
there are cars , motorbikes , industrial light and heavy vehicles .
in addition to the cost of repair parts , it takes into account the time valued by the manufacturer or the scales of paint .
this tool comes in line with its use , for each estimate .
the higher cost of 5.75 euros , for customers who use a little , the maximum 10 times per month .
then every insurance company , which operates the thousands of expertise , is negotiating a price with audatex .
other products , such as audavin , allow the full identification of a vehicle and equipment with which it came out of the assembly line , only by the number of windows .
audaglass focuses on the glass of cars , and audasubastas is an internet server opened to the professional sector , which has enchérir on vehicles declared wrecks .
his office of statistics is very helpful to identify those trends , conducting tests géo-démographiques or knowledge of the current problems by mark or model .
it is possible to study , for example , how many models of a determined went in the garage to mark a failure or how many have suffered serious disasters for a certain period .
motivates gt is the only spanish company which is devoted to the development of this kind of tools .
it is selling , among other things , gt estimate , which is also aimed at experts and provides digital images , as well as access to documents , official price and time of the manufacturer .
