vintage cars can be réenregistrées complex , although they have now been withdrawn , after steps .
estimate of a garage in four stages
with the auda-taller tool , the company audatex ensures that the user gets an estimate in just four steps : identifying the vehicle , seeking the room to spare , creating an estimate and the engineer .
the ease of use is a key element of these systems , above all to convince the older workers , to a greater or lesser extent , are resistant to the use of new management techniques .
the database includes 1 034 , 666 of cars , 109 tout-terrains , 137 motorcycles , 78 vans and 44 trucks .
naturally , in order to use it , a computer and connection to the internet are needed .
once the model to repair identified thanks to its number of windows , a graphic image model in question is can we really necessary selects the room .
